      • LOCALE_RB_SEARCH_PATTERN

        private static final java.util.regex.Pattern LOCALE_RB_SEARCH_PATTERN
        Regexp for searching locale properties files (with extension .properties). For example, text

        Locale_ch.properties

        will be found, but text

        some-file.xml

        won't be found.

      • RESOURCES_ROOT

        private static java.lang.String RESOURCES_ROOT
        Path to directory with resources. I don't put slash at the end, because it is everywhere between this constant and path to certain resource.

      • PRODUCT_VERSION

        private static java.lang.String PRODUCT_VERSION
        Field for build version. It looks like this: 
        1.23.40
        Description for numbers:
        1. GLOBAL VERSION. It's number of realize with many differences.
        2. COMMIT VERSION. It's number of "git commit"s.
        3. BUILD VERSION. After each launch of Ant build script this number increments by one.
